<!-- templates/budget-planner/how-to-use.hbs -->
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <style>
    @page {
      size: A4;
      margin: 12mm;
    }

    body {
      font-family: {{customization.fontFamily}};
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }

    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      border-bottom: 3px solid {{customization.primaryColor}};
      padding-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .title {
      font-size: 24px;
      color: {{customization.primaryColor}};
      margin-bottom: 3px;
    }

    .subtitle {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
    }

    .time-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background: {{customization.primaryColor}};
      color: white;
      padding: 5px 15px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      font-size: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .section {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: {{customization.primaryColor}};
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .weekly-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .week-card {
      background: #f8f9fa;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 3px solid {{customization.primaryColor}};
    }

    .week-label {
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #666;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }

    .week-task {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #333;
      min-height: 36px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .week-time {
      font-size: 10px;
      color: {{customization.secondaryColor}};
      margin-top: 5px;
    }

    .checklist-box {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, {{customization.primaryColor}}10, {{customization.secondaryColor}}10);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .checklist-title {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: {{customization.primaryColor}};
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .checklist-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 6px;
    }

    .check-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 6px 8px;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 6px;
    }

    .checkbox {
      width: 16px;
      height: 16px;
      border: 2px solid {{customization.primaryColor}};
      border-radius: 3px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-top: 1px;
    }

    .check-text {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #444;
    }

    .monthly-section {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .monthly-box {
      border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 12px;
    }

    .monthly-box.start {
      border-color: #4caf50;
      background: #e8f5e9;
    }

    .monthly-box.end {
      border-color: #ff9800;
      background: #fff3e0;
    }

    .monthly-title {
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
    }

    .monthly-box.start .monthly-title { color: #2e7d32; }
    .monthly-box.end .monthly-title { color: #ef6c00; }

    .monthly-list {
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #555;
      padding-left: 15px;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .monthly-list li {
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .tips-section {
      background: #fff8e1;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 12px;
    }

    .tips-title {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #f57c00;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .tips-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .tip-card {
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
      font-size: 10px;
    }

    .tip-icon {
      font-size: 16px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .tip-text {
      color: #555;
    }

    .tip-text strong {
      color: #333;
    }

    .footer-quote {
      margin-top: 12px;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 10px;
      background: {{customization.primaryColor}};
      color: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1 class="title">How to Use This Planner</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Your weekly routine for financial success</p>
  </div>

  <div style="text-align: center;">
    <span class="time-badge">Just 15 minutes per week</span>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">Your Weekly Money Date</div>
    <div class="weekly-grid">
      <div class="week-card">
        <div class="week-label">Week 1</div>
        <div class="week-task">Review last week's spending</div>
        <div class="week-time">5 min</div>
      </div>
      <div class="week-card">
        <div class="week-label">Week 2</div>
        <div class="week-task">Update "Actual" column in budget</div>
        <div class="week-time">5 min</div>
      </div>
      <div class="week-card">
        <div class="week-label">Week 3</div>
        <div class="week-task">Check savings goal progress</div>
        <div class="week-time">3 min</div>
      </div>
      <div class="week-card">
        <div class="week-label">Week 4</div>
        <div class="week-task">Plan next month's adjustments</div>
        <div class="week-time">5 min</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="checklist-box">
    <div class="checklist-title">Weekly Check-In (pick a day and stick to it!)</div>
    <div class="checklist-grid">
      <div class="check-item">
        <div class="checkbox"></div>
        <span class="check-text">Review this week's expenses in tracker</span>
      </div>
      <div class="check-item">
        <div class="checkbox"></div>
        <span class="check-text">Update "Actual" amounts in budget</span>
      </div>
      <div class="check-item">
        <div class="checkbox"></div>
        <span class="check-text">Check if any bills are due this week</span>
      </div>
      <div class="check-item">
        <div class="checkbox"></div>
        <span class="check-text">Transfer money to savings (if able)</span>
      </div>
      <div class="check-item">
        <div class="checkbox"></div>
        <span class="check-text">Celebrate one small win this week!</span>
      </div>
      <div class="check-item">
        <div class="checkbox"></div>
        <span class="check-text">Set one intention for next week</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="monthly-section">
    <div class="monthly-box start">
      <div class="monthly-title">Start of Month</div>
      <ul class="monthly-list">
        <li>Fill in "Planned" column for income & expenses</li>
        <li>Write your 3 priorities for the month</li>
        <li>Set a specific expense to reduce this month</li>
        <li>Review subscriptions ‚Äî cancel unused ones</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="monthly-box end">
      <div class="monthly-title">End of Month</div>
      <ul class="monthly-list">
        <li>Complete the reflection box</li>
        <li>Calculate total income vs expenses</li>
        <li>Update savings goal progress bars</li>
        <li>Carry lessons into next month's plan</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="tips-section">
    <div class="tips-title">Pro Tips for Success</div>
    <div class="tips-grid">
      <div class="tip-card">
        <span class="tip-icon">üì±</span>
        <span class="tip-text"><strong>Set a recurring reminder</strong> ‚Äî Same day, same time each week (Sunday evening works great)</span>
      </div>
      <div class="tip-card">
        <span class="tip-icon">‚òï</span>
        <span class="tip-text"><strong>Make it enjoyable</strong> ‚Äî Grab a coffee, put on music. It's a date with your future self.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="tip-card">
        <span class="tip-icon">‚úèÔ∏è</span>
        <span class="tip-text"><strong>Write in pencil</strong> ‚Äî Plans change. That's okay. Erase and adjust.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="tip-card">
        <span class="tip-icon">üéâ</span>
        <span class="tip-text"><strong>Celebrate small wins</strong> ‚Äî Paid a bill on time? That counts. Saved $20? Victory.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="footer-quote">
    "The best budget is one you'll actually use. Done is better than perfect."
  </div>
</body>

</html>
